, decay, and reinvention. Building Legends Academy Pakistan now feels like participating consciously in that cycle of Pakistan’s development journey, if even in a small way. Above all, I hope the students left with a sense of optimism for Pakistan, recognising the boundless opportunities here rather than contributing to the brain drain. And if I didn’t bore them… perhaps I’ll be invited back. (The talk has been recorded & happy to share the link — just DM me).",
